OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779872683
OL,3,CPolice arrest six as part of
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour crackdown over
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FKent Police arrested six people and
OL,8,Fissued dispersal orders as part of a
OL,9,Fcrackdown on antisocial behaviour over
OL,10,Fthe bank holiday weekend.
OL,12,FThe force applied Section 34 dispersal
OL,13,Forders across Broadstairs, Margate and
OL,14,FRamsgate to address issues, such as
OL,15,Funderage street drinking and criminal
OL,16,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
