OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779872683
OL,3,CPolice arrest six as part of
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour crackdown over
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FOfficers also made a number of
OL,8,Farrests, including in Broadstairs
OL,9,Fwhere one teenager was detained for
OL,10,Fassaulting an emergency worker and
OL,11,Fpossession of cannabis.
OL,13,FA second was arrested for being drunk
OL,14,Fand disorderly, while another was
OL,15,Fapprehended for breaching a dispersal
OL,16,Forder.
OL,18,FThe force said it had deployed extra
OL,19,Fpatrols to cope with the influx of
OL,20,Fvisitors, which was boosted by record
OL,21,FMay temperatures for the UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779872683
OL,3,CPolice arrest six as part of
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour crackdown over
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FChief Inspector Ian Swallow said: "We
OL,8,Fknew there would be thousands of
OL,9,Fvisitors across Thanet during the bank
OL,10,Fholiday weekend and had plans in place
OL,11,Fto tackle any possible antisocial
OL,12,Fbehaviour head-on.
OL,14,F"The vast majority of those visitors
OL,15,Fwere respectful and enjoyed their
OL,16,Ftime, however there will always be
OL,17,Fpockets of incidents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779872683
OL,3,CPolice arrest six as part of
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour crackdown over
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,F"Officers were out in the community
OL,8,Fmeeting and talking to residents,
OL,9,Fvisitors and business owners and we
OL,10,Fmade sure that patrols were deployed
OL,11,Facross Thanet to ensure that officers
OL,12,Fwere nearby to deal with any
OL,13,Fdisruption that took place.
OL,15,F"Our plans ensured that crime and
OL,16,Fdisorder was kept to an absolute
OL,17,Fminimum which is shown by the low
OL,18,Fnumber of arrests, and when incidents
OL,19,Fdid arise officers were able to
OL,20,Fquickly identify those involved."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
